0.2.3
  * Throttle worker process restarts if the last attempt to start a worker was less than 5 seconds ago
  * Better error reporting, if worker fails to start on boot abort master with sigquit
  * Support flat object configuration files e.g. module.exports = { /* your config */ }
  * Add a default after_fork to ConfigLoader
0.2.2  
  * Added common logging methods internally logm and logw to support configurable logger output based on level 'debug','info', 'error'
0.2.1
  * Set environment TIAMAT=1 for worker process e.g. process.env.TIAMAT
0.2.0
  * Allow loading apps using module.exports = app;
